1. A no soliciting sign on your door has no legal power. There has to be a clear line a person has to cross before they get to the door. <br>
2. You can't shoot at children who cross into your property, even if they're trespassing.<br>
3. Courts tend to treat back and side yards differently from front yards.<br>
4. In a life threatening emergency your property rights are gener<span class="substr"> </span></p></div>
